WEBVTT

00:04:56.280 --> 00:05:00.336
The end of the evening,
they head for home and for bed.

00:05:00.360 --> 00:05:03.576
In the morning, Claire calls up to Vera

00:05:03.600 --> 00:05:06.040
and says she's going out to breakfast.

00:05:07.080 --> 00:05:10.336
When she returns a short while later,

00:05:10.360 --> 00:05:12.336
Vera wasn't up.

00:05:12.360 --> 00:05:15.376
She pulls back the covers

00:05:15.400 --> 00:05:18.000
and makes the gruesome discovery.

00:05:18.720 --> 00:05:20.840
Vera was dead.

00:05:22.240 --> 00:05:24.576
When it comes to Spanish flu,

00:05:24.600 --> 00:05:26.816
those stories are common,

00:05:26.840 --> 00:05:30.376
of lightning speed deaths.